## 7. 调用示例

假设外部 API 返回的是中国时区时间，但字符串里没有带 `+08:00`：

```python
payload = {
    "name": "测试数据",
    "start_time": "2026-06-05 12:30:00",
    "end_time": "2026-06-05T15:00:00+08:00",
    "unknown_api_field": "abc",
}

record.with_context(
    safe_external_json=True,
    external_datetime_to_utc=True,
    external_source_tz="Asia/Shanghai",
).write(payload)
```

写入结果大概是：

```python
{
    "start_time": "2026-06-05 04:30:00",
    "end_time": "2026-06-05 07:00:00",
}
```

`unknown_api_field` 不会写入，会进入日志。

